name: The Sun Print
description:
I was inspired to make three tarot card prints, none of which turned out to be tarot cards themselves. Still, I ended up with The Moon, The Sun, and The Star.

 

In tarot, The Sun is part of the Major Arcana and when drawn upright, it signifies good fortune, happiness, joy, and harmony. It represents the universe coming together and agreeing with your path and aiding forward movement into something greater.

 

These are full color giclee prints, printed on fine art paper with a matte finish. They’re nice and thick with a hint texture to them.

name: Arches National Park Sticker
description:
3.5 x 3.5 inches

 

My National Park collection is perfect for anybody who loves (or even mildly likes) to travel.  They're perfect to stick to cars, hydro flasks, laptops, and planners. I did my best to keep the designs simple while still ringing true to the scenery.  One special touch is that I included the state flower for where the national parks are located.  Arches National Park is in Utah, so the flowers you see in the design are the Sego Lily.

 

Each National Park sticker comes in two background colors and two design colors. The two design colors are always either black or white, but the background choices vary depending on the park. This listing is for Arches, so the background colors are Saddle (a tan that pulls orangish yellow) or Burnt Umber (a rich and dark reddish brown).

  • Removable and replaceable
  • Waterproof

name: Clear Book Sticker
description:
3 x 2.81 inches

 

I am what my family likes to call a "voracious reader."  When I get a book in my hands, I instantly become entranced by it, unable to do almost anything but read until I finally finish it.  It's not uncommon for me to forget to eat or sleep with a good book in front of me.  Is it healthy? Not really.  Would I want it any other way? Never.  For this sticker, I chose to focus on some of the more mainstream classics that I'm confident almost everybody has heard of:

 

Emma
Jane Eyre
Pride and Prejudice
Gone with the Wind
Sense and Sensibility
Great Expectations
Wuthering Heights

 

 

  • Glossy finish
  • UV protected laminate to protect stickers from weather and sunlight
  • 2-4 year outdoor life
  • Waterproof
  • Dishwasher safe, can be placed on cars and water bottles
  • Removes with little to no residue, any residue can be easily removed with hand sanitizer or rubbing alcohol

name: Divine Feminine Print
description:
I was inspired to call this Divine Feminine because of the beautiful, soft edges of the female figure that I based the drawing on, but I hope that regardless of gender it represents how powerful it is to own every inch of your body.  I edited the original design with two more skin tones so that hopefully more people will be able to recognize themselves in the piece.  You can pick which skin tone and size print you would like from the drop down menus.

 

This is a full color print, printed on premium photo paper with a smooth matte finish that you won't leave finger prints on.

 

Available in two sizes:
5x7
8x10

 

*Listing pictures are Light and Medium*

name: Reading Quote Print
description:
I struggled to learn how to read.  Throughout kindergarten and first grade, I would be taken out of my normal classes and brought to a special room in the school where I, and a couple other students, got targeted attention to help us.  I always think about how funny it is that I struggled so hard to learn to read and it quickly became one of my favorite things to do.  Once I learned how to do it, and it finally made sense, I couldn't be stopped.  I became a voracious reader and now, as a twenty-something, I still can, and prefer to, get lost in a story and forget who I am.  That is why this quote means so much to me, and why I think this is probably the best thing I've ever made.

 

This is a full color print, printed on premium photo paper with a smooth matte finish that you won't leave finger prints on.

 

Available in two sizes:
5x7
8x10
